{"tid":1962063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣大舉向日本提供口罩佢人道支援","createTime":"2020-04-07T08:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T15:55:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74a66d262d0ee8e2441731bd82b688ed110ec337","tid":1962063,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2020040700868&amp;g=int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiji.com%2Fjc%2Farticle%3Fk%3D2020040700868%26g%3Dint&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=1464f48c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2020040700868&amp;g=int</a><br />\n<br />\n台湾、日本にもマスク寄贈検討　新型コロナで人道支援外交<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n【台北時事】台湾外交部（外務省）は７日の記者会見で、新型コロナウイルスの感染が拡大し、マスク不足が続く日本に対し、医療用マスクを寄贈する検討を始めたことを明らかにした。<br />\n　台湾は人道支援外交の一環で、感染が深刻な米国や欧州各国などに計１０００万枚の医療用マスクを無償供与することを決定済み。第２弾の支援対象国に日本を含めることを検討している。"},{"pid":"6fd836b66063720c455540b1bb639392772d68de","tid":1962063,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:42:50.000Z","msg":"口交部出聲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8099131dc6f12dc47ceb0049e55887c52f205817","tid":1962063,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd836b66063720c455540b1bb639392772d68de","tid":1962063,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:42:50.000Z","msg":"口交部出聲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af88054789ad989a8949824255534ed21423a74e","tid":1962063,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"不爽"},{"pid":"35b2f4c4782a25cd16ce873977dfe276e7d0dc17","t